retz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-145/0000018d-f089-d7f4-a3dd-f68d05d70000</link><description>哈马斯政治局主席哈尼亚表示，该组织在释放人质/停火谈判方面持灵活态度，但已做好继续战斗的准备，并呼吁穆斯林在斋月第一天加固阿克萨清真寺。 ■ 以色列国防军：160 包人道主义援助物资空投到叙利亚加沙南部 ■ 哈马斯和法塔赫代表团将于周四在莫斯科会面，讨论组建统一的巴勒斯坦政府 ■ 战争结束 145 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-145/0000018d-f089-d7f4-a3dd-f68d05d70000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦外长表示与哈马斯关于统一政府的谈判预计不会出现“奇迹”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/palestinian-seminister-no-miracles-expected-at-talks-on-unified-government/0000018d-f04e-dd8a-a5af-f87ecf160000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总理穆罕默德·什塔耶辞职几天后，哈马斯和法塔赫的代表定于周四在莫斯科举行会谈</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/palestinian-seminister-no-miracles-expected-at-talks-on-unified-government/0000018d-f04e-dd8a-a5af-f87ecf160000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 解释道：美国强大且分裂的亲以色列游说团体的内幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aipac-explained-the-inside-story-of-americas-powerful-and-divisive-pro-israel-lobby/0000018d-e4ac-d972-a5bf-efaf96c60000</link><description>美国以色列公共事务委员会与美国总统和政客发生冲突、纵容、针对和支持，使以色列成为一个日益党派化的问题。以下是您需要了解的有关 AIPAC 的信息，这是一个令人尊敬、令人恐惧和谩骂的游说和政治筹款组织，准备在 2024 年的选举中发挥巨大作用</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aipac-explained-the-inside-story-of-americas-powerful-and-divisive-pro-israel-lobby/0000018d-e4ac-d972-a5bf-efaf96c60000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦-以色列和平活动家二人组被《时代》杂志评为年度女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-israeli-peace-activist-duo-named-among-time-magazines-women-of-the-year/0000018d-f04a-dd0a-afcf-ffde7c740000</link><description>“妇女争取和平”和“太阳妇女”这两个组织形成了所谓的“伙伴关系协定”，誓言“坚定、坚持和相互尊重地共同努力”，以结束以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:42:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-israeli-peace-activist-duo-named-among-time-magazines-women-of-the-year/0000018d-f04a-dd0a-afcf-ffde7c740000</guid></item><item><title>《欣快感》明星在接受拜登采访时抗议以色列和加沙战争时被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/euphoria-star-arrested-while-protesting-against-israel-war-in-gaza-at-biden-interview/0000018d-efd4-dd0a-afcf-efd698060000</link><description>在 JVP Instagram 上分享的一篇帖子中，亨特·谢弗 (Hunter Schafer) 与其他示威者坐在一起，身穿印有“立即停火”字样的 T 恤。该组织还发布了抗议视频，视频中女演员和其他人高呼“不再有武器，不再有战争，停火是我们奋斗的目标”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/euphoria-star-arrested-while-protesting-against-israel-war-in-gaza-at-biden-interview/0000018d-efd4-dd0a-afcf-efd698060000</guid></item><item><title>向以色列高等法院提交请愿书，反对教育部长不授予以色列奖的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/high-court-petition-filed-against-education-ministers-decision-not-to-award-israel-prize/0000018d-f01e-dd8a-a5af-f87e2cb70000</link><description>请愿书认为，根据以色列奖项规定，教育部长无权取消奖项类别。 “对这些决定的唯一不幸的解释是教育部长接管该奖项的尝试是完全不可接受的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/high-court-petition-filed-against-education-ministers-decision-not-to-award-israel-prize/0000018d-f01e-dd8a-a5af-f87e2cb70000</guid></item><item><title>该国的宗教右翼意识形态正在以色列造成劳动力紧缩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/the-states-religious-right-ideology-is-creating-a-labor-crunch-in-israel/0000018d-f032-d7f4-a3dd-f63ee6870000</link><description>多年来，以色列经济的快速增长