0</guid></item><item><title>以色列地方选举：极端正统派、极右派在全国各地取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</link><description>极端正统派和极右宗教犹太复国主义政党将在耶路撒冷取得压倒性胜利，而南部城市米兹佩·拉蒙将迎来一位以极右观点闻名的利库德集团市长。特拉维夫和海法仍然是自由派的据点</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列定居者因西岸暴力风险将继续被拘留，未经审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</link><description>以色列国防部长决定，由于阿里尔·达尼诺 (Ariel Danino) 可能在约旦河西岸煽动暴力，继 10 月份首次被拘留后，他将被再行政拘留三个月</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:51:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯之间的人质释放、停火谈判立场如何？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯都有兴趣在下个月斋月开始前达成释放人质的协议，但尽管最近几天的乐观情绪仍然存在，但仍然存在许多障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军坦克至少五次错误地向以色列领土开火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</link><description>有一次，以色列和黎巴嫩边境沿线的哈尼塔集体农场发射了两枚炮弹，炸毁了两栋房屋；另一次，在加沙发射的一枚炮弹击中了斯德洛特市政厅。以色列国防军回应：“吸取了必要的教训”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</guid></item></channel></rss>